levant stakeholders to ensure accuracy and clarity.\n   - Finalize the audit report and distribute it to appropriate parties.\n\n7. **Follow-Up**:\n   - Develop an action plan to address the recommendations made in the audit report.\n   - Monitor the implementation of corrective actions.\n   - Conduct follow-up audits if necessary to ensure that issues have been resolved.\n\nThroughout the audit process, it is important to maintain clear communication, document all procedures and findings, and adhere to relevant standards and guidelines. If you have specific requirements or need more detailed information on any of these steps, please let me know!","additional_kwargs":{},"response_metadata":{"finish_reason":"stop"},"type":"AIMessageChunk","name":null,"id":"run-2cb6b1f6-12f1-478f-8cee-13da00ca92dd","example":false,"tool_calls":[],"invalid_tool_calls":[],"tool_call_chunks":[]}}]],"llm_output":null,"run":null}},{"op":"add","path":"/logs/AzureChatOpenAI/end_time","value":"2025-06-24T15:09:42.345+00:00"}]}

